{"tid":964373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"門戶大開！夜店正妹神秘地帶「大走光」　網暴動：可惡想撕","createTime":"2019-01-01T09:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T09:35:01.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb52c8112b29e299effb3ad7ef2e3fd37b2fe7d","tid":964373,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"辣妹最愛穿著緊身服裝，顯露出姣好身材，牛仔熱褲更是衣櫥裡面的必備百搭單品。有網友就分享一張「門戶大開」的照片，詢問大家「這是什麼人設計？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/30/1712491-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F1712491-XXL.jpg&h=27cd186a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網友在臉書社團「爆廢公社」發文，她分享一張照片，並詢問大家「這是什麼人設計？」只見照片中一名身材相當火辣的女子，上身穿著黑色平口小可愛，露出一截纖纖小蠻腰，下半身卻穿著一件「貼心設計」的牛仔熱褲，左半邊私密處幾乎全部露出來，令人感到相當匪夷所思。<br />\n<br />\n網友們看完紛紛留言，「義大利名設計師，西湯普利司設計的」、「好像被強X完的褲」、「可惡！想撕」、「方便深入了解內在」、「很好插入」、「Mr.Fuck me 設計，這樣你才能直接來」，還有網友搞笑回，「其實剛才有男生不小心太大力撕破了！」"},{"pid":"9bafb100227ad36082c993dcd83c90ece0875e15","tid":964373,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b9b749a2d60aa9f071befa90437e0d4affed12","tid":964373,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bafb100227ad36082c993dcd83c90ece0875e15","tid":964373,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"走開留返畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89c89b601f65dbb730dc4402840721f043e9f08","tid":964373,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"仲纜皮帶做埋<br />\n<br />\n唔至在啦"},{"pid":"08cd6529